vernac_cmds: Lemma conj_nonexpansive {A} `{ageable A} : forall (F G:pred A -> pred A), nonexpansive F -> nonexpansive G -> nonexpansive (fun x:pred A => F x && G x).
Lemma conj_contractive {A} `{ageable A} : forall F G, contractive F -> contractive G -> contractive (fun x => F x && G x).
Lemma impl_contractive {A} `{ageable A} : forall F G, contractive F -> contractive G -> contractive (fun x => F x --> G x).
Lemma impl_nonexpansive {A} `{ageable A} : forall F G, nonexpansive F -> nonexpansive G -> nonexpansive (fun x => F x --> G x).
Lemma forall_contractive {A} `{ageable A} : forall B (X : pred A -> B -> pred A), (forall x, (contractive (fun y => X y x))) -> contractive (fun x => (allp (X x))).
Lemma forall_nonexpansive {A} `{ageable A} : forall B (X : pred A -> B -> pred A), (forall x, (nonexpansive (fun y => X y x))) -> nonexpansive (fun x => (allp (X x))).
Lemma exists_contractive {A} `{ageable A} : forall B (X : pred A -> B -> pred A), (forall x, (contractive (fun y => X y x))) -> contractive (fun x => (exp (X x))).
Lemma exists_nonexpansive {A} `{ageable A} : forall B (X : pred A -> B -> pred A), (forall x, (nonexpansive (fun y => X y x))) -> nonexpansive (fun x => (exp (X x))).
Lemma later_contractive {A} `{ageable A} : forall F, nonexpansive F -> contractive (fun X => (|>(F X))).
Lemma const_nonexpansive {A: Type} {H: ageable A}: forall P: pred A, nonexpansive (fun _ => P).
Lemma const_contractive {A: Type} {H: ageable A}: forall P: pred A, contractive (fun _ => P).
Lemma identity_nonexpansive {A: Type} {H: ageable A}: nonexpansive (fun P: pred A => P).
Lemma contractive_nonexpansive {A} `{ageable A} : forall F, contractive F -> nonexpansive F.
Lemma sepcon_contractive {A} {JA: Join A}{PA: Perm_alg A}{SA: Sep_alg A}{AG: ageable A}{XA: Age_alg A} : forall F G, contractive F -> contractive G -> contractive (fun x => F x * G x).
Lemma sepcon_nonexpansive {A}{JA: Join A}{PA: Perm_alg A}{SA: Sep_alg A}{AG: ageable A}{XA: Age_alg A} : forall F G, nonexpansive F -> nonexpansive G -> nonexpansive (fun x => F x * G x).
Lemma wand_contractive {A} {JA: Join A}{PA: Perm_alg A}{SA: Sep_alg A}{AG: ageable A}{XA: Age_alg A} : forall F G, contractive F -> contractive G -> contractive (fun x => F x -* G x).
Lemma wand_nonexpansive {A} {JA: Join A}{PA: Perm_alg A}{SA: Sep_alg A}{AG: ageable A}{XA: Age_alg A} : forall F G, nonexpansive F -> nonexpansive G -> nonexpansive (fun x => F x -* G x).
Lemma prove_contractive {A} `{ageable A} : forall F, (forall P Q, |>(P >=> Q) |-- F P >=> F Q) -> contractive F.
Lemma prove_HOcontractive1 {A} `{ageable A} : forall X F, (forall P Q: X -> pred A, (ALL x:X, |>(P x >=> Q x) |-- ALL x:X, F P x >=> F Q x)) -> HOcontractive F.
Lemma prove_HOcontractive {A} `{ageable A} : forall X F, (forall (P Q: X -> pred A) (x: X), (ALL x:X, (|> P x <=> |> Q x) |-- F P x >=> F Q x)) -> HOcontractive F.

Lemma HORec_sub {A} `{ageable A} : forall G B (F : pred A -> (B -> pred A) -> B -> pred A) (HF1 : forall X, HOcontractive (F X)) (HF2 : forall R a P Q, P >=> Q |-- F P R a >=> F Q R a) (HF3 : forall P Q X, ALL b:B, |>(P b >=> Q b) |-- ALL b:B, F X P b >=> F X Q b), forall P Q, G |-- P >=> Q -> G |-- ALL b:B, HORec (F P) b >=> HORec (F Q) b.

rewrite HORec_fold_unfold in H3 by auto.
specialize ( HF3 (HORec (F P)) (HORec (F Q)) P a H4 b a').
